            These @X09<@X0EJ@X09>@X03oin subfunctions are available:

               @X0E(@X0CA@X0E)@X03uto-join configuration update
               @X0E(@X0CL@X0E)@X03ocate conference by keywords
               @X0E(@X0CM@X0E)@X03ain board
               @X0E(@X0CN@X0E)@X03ew message status
               @X0E(@X0CS@X0E)@X03tatus of all conferences
               @X0E(@X0C+@X0E)@X03next higher conference
               @X0E(@X0C-@X0E)@X03next lower conference


