            "header" and the first 72 characters of message text.

@X09<@X0EQQ@X09>@X03uicker  Displays a Quicker summary of the mail messages which are
            available for reading @X0E(@X0Cdisplays only the message header.@X0E)@X03

            These commands have nothing to do with the speed messages
            are displayed ฤฤ this is based solely upon your modem.
            If you wish to "capture" or "log" some messages, examine
            the @X09<@X0ENS@X09>@X03 Non-Stop feature, BUT be careful to select a
            reasonable range or you may find yourself very short on
            disk space and very long on phone bill.


